{"tid":2212280,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"AMD之後，英特爾據報已獲向華為供貨許可","createTime":"2020-09-21T16:14:40.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-23T06:46:09.000Z","uid":91914,"like":7,"dislike":50,"uniUserReply":33,"replies":[{"pid":"8a9bc26d59e6f727ed621c46f4e467f5e23bad47","tid":2212280,"uid":91914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:14:40.000Z","msg":"內地傳媒引述英特爾(Intel)證實，已經獲得向華為供貨許可，因此其已在繼續推進華為的手提電腦專案。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n報道稱，英特爾是最早一批拿到許可的企業。華為則表示，去年底英特爾拿到的許可，不受今年兩次制裁的影響<br />\n。<br />\n外國媒體早前報道，美國晶片商超微(AMD)已經獲得向華為供貨的許可證，預計不會因美國對華為的禁令，而對業務產生重大影響。<br />\n<br />\n隨英特爾及AMD外，據悉美光、三星、SK海力士、台積電、聯發科、中芯國際(00981)等廠商早前均表明，已向美國商務部申請向華為繼續供貨的許可證。"},{"pid":"1c455321734d8c29d6249e1ace2441d3bcd579db","tid":2212280,"uid":36134,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:16:47.000Z","msg":"喂 喂 <br />\n大豆侵你唔係撚啊嘛<br />\n最起碼台積電唔供得貨"},{"pid":"3998f22a2d24e0f580f963096cef2ccf72ede8f2","tid":2212280,"uid":4243,"like":30,"dislike":1,"score":29,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:17:16.000Z","msg":"HSBC有冇諗過自己會快過華為先走<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c8f73fa040bd7c02f5fd77eb6b8678b80f4fc644","tid":2212280,"uid":241504,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:19:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aaf927733de9a275a276357edcdc4954356e73ec","tid":2212280,"uid":293617,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:21:33.000Z","msg":"入返D AMD股先,PS5 XBOX,華為都買佢貨"},{"pid":"ea8242235355415d99d46212dcec61dc20cd57e5","tid":2212280,"uid":75072,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T16:26:19.000Z","msg":"手提電腦<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屎為整飽佢"},{"pid":"bf4fceecabb6a7dbf5788bb2417e29e99aee9fc5","tid":2212280,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":